						<div class="line"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="context-info">
						<h3>How are others solving similar challenges?</h3>
						<p>With a better understanding of our design challenges, I  looked for inspiration and relevant solutions in the wild. I conducted <em> market research</em> and presented existing solutions to both internal and client teams.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
