						</a>
						<span class="caption"><em>Market Research:</em> 
						</br>
						Short form video sites and music web apps were a major source for inspirtation. Best-in-class examples kept their content playing even while users explored new options. </span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="chapter">
