				<div class ="context">
					<div class="context-title">
						<h2>Promote Content</h2>
						<div class="line"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="context-info">
						<h3>Meet the users where they are.</h3>
						<p>One of the primary challenges was how to get users continuously watching more content. Our strategy: promote the right content in the right context. 
						</br></br>
						To understand what types of content to promote and when, I created a <em>content model</em> and mapped out relevant connections between video types. To inform the process, I asked our analytics team about viewing behavior trends on the current product. Both informed our navigation system and content structure within the video player experience. 
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
